usg: Use to set where to display the response from the form submit. This will override the target value of the owner form element.

vals.desc: Loads in the same frame. Default value
Loads the response in a new unnamed window/tab
Loads the response in the parent frame. If no parent will behave as _self
Loads the response in the top most frame. If no parent will behave as _self
The response is displayed in an iframe named with the given value.
